{"tid":326449,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"被指CIA　「可能我似Jason Bourne」","createTime":"2017-07-18T04:17:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-18T06:23:18.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fbf12eb23d8e1186d596ca6fb660b33184223446","tid":326449,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:17:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20093512&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170718\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20093512%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170718&d=%2F8JwxMpE5qC8u%2FkABUisAdWu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=d8776ae0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20093512%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170718&h=cb4c05ea\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20093512&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170718</a><br />\n<br />\n被指CIA　「可能我似Jason Bourne」<br />\n<br />\n要聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170718/large/a11a02a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170718%2Flarge%2Fa11a02a.jpg&h=8af42ccf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n6月30日晚大批親中人士包圍在場採訪的外國人，更伸出拳頭恐嚇，穿黑衣者是Richard Scotford同行的朋友。Lostdutch提供圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】Richard Scotford與朋友遭親中人士包圍指罵後，「愛港行動」召集人陳淨心在facebook指控他們是佔領中環「現場指揮」，更有人在WhatsApp流傳Richard是美國中情局（CIA）人員。本身是英國人的Richard幽默稱，從未去過美國，但可能有點像Jason Bourne（電影《叛諜追擊》男主角，由麥迪文飾演），或許因此被當作CIA。他建議對方至少應指控他是MI6（英國軍情六處）。<br />\nRichard在1996年來港，曾在酒吧工作、教授英文、經營生意。他對中國歷史感興趣，2010年在中文大學修畢中國研究碩士學位，專攻意見新聞（Opinion Journalism），也經常撰文記錄示威經歷和評論時事。<br />\n9.28雨傘運動爆發，警方向示威者首發的催淚彈正正在Richard上方爆開，他起初以為是煙霧，還叫示威者不用逃跑，當時不能相信警察以催淚彈對付示威者。警方施放一輪催淚彈後，有人開始唱Beyond的歌曲，令他畢生難忘。近年他深入採訪反水貨等示威，其facebook和twitter賬戶分別有近8,000人和1,300人追蹤。<br />\n■記者潘柏林<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n\t採訪民族黨集會遭親中者圍攻　英記者：文化大革命重臨<br />\n要聞 5小時前被指CIA　「可能我似Jason Bourne」"},{"pid":"cb1396f846789bc5b946e8f556dba979ce8a7f04","tid":326449,"uid":27363,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:26:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">警方施放一輪催淚彈後，有人開始唱Beyond的歌曲，令他畢生難忘。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12bd7e44d4180d93130e542bab7ebf4afa0fb4d8","tid":326449,"uid":50740,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:28:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">警方施放一輪催淚彈後，有人開始唱Beyond的歌曲，令他畢生難忘。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不要再說了,後悔咁柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2731a61745a610348377f792ee65dfab9836d30","tid":326449,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:29:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">警方施放一輪催淚彈後，有人開始唱Beyond的歌曲，令他畢生難忘。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不要再說了,後悔咁柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唉, 影衰晒<br />\n<br />\n外國人聽到, 真係完全唔能夠理解"},{"pid":"239ad3f987135a8fd78dcdea04ee7bb2143f4dc7","tid":326449,"uid":33864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:31:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/RichScotford5/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.l